    "faq_7adUCb": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "item_qY9WDx": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are they slip-resistant?",
            "content": "<p>The SOLYDIA MaxOne are <strong>SRC certified</strong>, the strictest slip-resistance standard in Europe.</p><p>This means they have been tested and approved on:</p><ul><li><strong>Wet tiled floors</strong> (SR)<br/></li><li><strong>Steel floors with glycerol</strong> (SC)<br/></li></ul><p>The <strong>SRC certification combines both tests</strong>, guaranteeing maximum grip on all surfaces — whether wet, greasy, or oily.</p><p>If your job requires slip-resistant footwear, the <strong>S3 standard fully meets those needs</strong>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_mwTVFL": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are they waterproof?",
            "content": "<p>The SOLYDIA are <strong>water-resistant</strong> and certified <strong>WR (Water Resistant)</strong>.</p><p>They provide effective protection against:</p><ul><li>Rain<br/></li><li>Water splashes<br/></li><li>Spills<br/></li><li>Wet surfaces</li></ul><p>Perfect for all jobs exposed to moisture.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_i4QnxY": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "For which environments are they suitable?",
            "content": "<p>The <strong>SOLYDIA </strong>are <strong>S3 certified</strong>, making them suitable for <strong>all demanding work environments</strong>:</p><p>✓ Hard floors (concrete, tiles, asphalt)<br/><br/>✓ Long periods of standing (6–12+ hours)<br/><br/>✓ Intensive walking (10,000+ steps/day)<br/><br/>✓ Handling heavy loads<br/><br/>✓ Wet or greasy surfaces (<strong>SRC certified</strong>)<br/><br/>✓ Risk of falling objects<br/><br/>✓ Risk of punctures</p><p>Whether you work indoors or outdoors, they <strong>meet all the requirements of S3 certification</strong>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_B3GKD4": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How does the rotary lacing system work?",
            "content": "<p>The rotary lacing system works with a dial: turn it clockwise to tighten the shoe and counterclockwise to loosen it. </p><p>This technology allows for <strong>precise, millimeter-accurate adjustment in just 2 seconds</strong>, offering much greater speed and accuracy compared to traditional laces.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_KMGGcp": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What’s the difference compared to my current safety shoes?",
            "content": "<p>Our sneakers are <strong>45% lighter</strong> than standard safety shoes while maintaining the same <strong>S3 protection</strong>.</p><p>The <strong>high-density Memory Foam insole</strong> eliminates foot pain, and the modern design looks just like real sneakers. You get the <strong>same level of safety</strong> with <strong>revolutionary comfort and style</strong>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_acrVmw": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do SOLYDIA really comply with the S3 standard?",
            "content": "<p>Our sneakers are <strong>certified according to the European standard EN ISO 20345 S3</strong>, which guarantees a <strong>steel toe cap resistant to 200 Joules of impact</strong>, a <strong>Kevlar anti-puncture sole</strong>, <strong>water resistance</strong>, and <strong>anti-static properties</strong>.</p><p>All tests are <strong>validated by independent certification bodies</strong>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_qUkwx3": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I wear them all day without pain?",
            "content": "<p>The <strong>high-density Memory Foam insole</strong> and <strong>lightweight construction</strong> are specially designed for long workdays.</p><p>Our sneakers have been tested during <strong>12-hour consecutive shifts</strong>. If you experience any discomfort, we offer a <strong>full 30-day money-back guarantee</strong>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_cYzQ4M": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Does the sneaker-style design hold up on construction sites?",
            "content": "<p>Although designed with a sneaker look, our shoes use <strong>high-strength industrial materials</strong>: reinforced mesh, sealed stitching, and a professional slip-resistant sole.</p><p>They <strong>resist mud, dust, and splashes</strong> while remaining <strong>easy to clean</strong>.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_7U4jC7": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I choose my size?",
            "content": "<p>If you are between two sizes, we recommend <strong>choosing the larger size for extra comfort</strong>.</p><p>Check out our <strong>detailed size guide with measurements in centimeters</strong>, available below the product photos.</p>"
          }
        },
        "item_AgGyix": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Warranty & Returns",
            "content": "<p>Our <strong>12-month warranty</strong> covers all manufacturing and material defects. Normal wear and tear from daily use is not covered.</p><p>If there’s an issue, simply send us a <strong>photo and a description</strong>, and we will provide a <strong>free replacement</strong> if the defect is confirmed.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
